enhanced_by.reason: Both methods require a Locale and a path-like input (URL in addUrl, Path in addPath).
Both methods update the internal state of the FakeValuesService by adding or updating locale-specific data.
After adding a URL, the method fetchObject can be used to retrieve the data loaded from the URL, similar to how data is fetched from the internal state.
Similar to fetchObject, fetch can be used to retrieve specific data points from the newly added URL data.
